[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ねえ、式典に出るのにこの服でいいと思う？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00224",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うーん、でもお母さん、ランツェさんみたいに\n正装を窮屈がらない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00225",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "まあ、それは窮屈かも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00226",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "聞いたわよ。\n果ての大陸到達を祈願しての記念式典があるって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00227",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "あっ……！　その声は！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00228",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "久しぶりね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00229",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ヨハナちゃん！　裁判終わったの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00230",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "ううん、まだ終わってないわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00231",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "月影の会の起こした事件は大規模だし、\nまだまだ何年もかかると思うな……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00232",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "ええ。傷つけた人たちへの謝罪だって、\nこれからも続けていくつもり",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00233",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "そっか……しっかり、向き合ってるんだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00234",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "……当然ながら、相手の反応は様々だけどね。\nその途中で、小耳に挟んだの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00235",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "レスナ、あんたたちがもう一度果ての大陸へ\n挑戦するってね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00236",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "だったら、この天才の力が必要でしょ？\nアタシもついていくわよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00237",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "わぁ……！　嬉しいよ！！\nでも、本当にいいの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00238",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "おじいちゃんが「行ってきなさい、\nそして自分が正しいと思うことをしなさい」ってさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00239",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "話を聞いた時の私の顔を見て、\n背中を押してくれたんだと思う",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00240",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "でもヨハナ、強くなったアタシについてこれるかな～？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00241",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "その身で鴉の技、また体感してみる？　騎士団員さん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00242",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "レスナ、もしかしてこの子が、\nあなたがよく話していた大切なお友達の……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00243",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、そうだよお母さん。\nこちら、友達のヨハナちゃん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00244",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "えっ、レスナのお母さん……？\nウソ、若い、お姉さんにしか見えないわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00245",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "まあ……！　私、ヨハナちゃん気に入っちゃった！\nとってもいい子ね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00246",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "もう、お母さんったら……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00247",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "改めましてヨハナちゃん、レスナの母のメーヴェよ。\nこれから果ての大陸まで、一緒によろしくね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00248",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "よ、よろしくお願いします……\nというか、お母さんも船に乗るんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00249",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ええ。レスナから聞いてるかもしれないけど、\n私は夫のユリウス……レスナのお父さんを探しているの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00250",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "確か、頂獣ウェルテックスの攻撃で\n行方不明になったっていう……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00251",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "そう、それで世界中探しても見つかってなくて。\nそれでね、思い当たったのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00252",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "もしかしてあの人、\n果ての大陸にいるんじゃないかなって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00253",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "ウェルテックスの能力を考えると、\nその可能性も否定できないよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00254",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "でもさすがに私一人じゃ果ての大陸には行けないし、\nレスナの船旅にご一緒したいな～って",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00255",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……とまあ、このような母ですが\n冒険者としての腕は確かですので",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00256",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "親子ともども、仲良くしてね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00257",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "はい、それはもう……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00258",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（レスナの母親……愉快で、大きい海みたいな人）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00259",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "天才を自称する、レスナの友達の少女。\n祖父の裁判のため、別行動していた",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]